nodes.text: In 27 ABY during the Yuuzhan Vong War, New Republic Senator Viqi Shesh organized a Yuuzhan Vong assassination attempt against Chief of State Borsk Fey'lya. It occurred during the unveiling of the YVH-Series battle droid by Tendrando Arms, though the assassins were defeated by members of Fey'lya's party, with the aid of YVH 1.
